```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(move)
```

```{r}
amwo_data <- getMovebankData(study = "American Woodcock Migration Ecology in Eastern North America", login = readRDS("movebank_credentials.rds"), timestamp_start = "20170801000000000", timestamp_end = "20220225000000000", removeDuplicatedTimestamps=TRUE) %>% as.data.frame() #20190115000000000
```

```{r}
#make sure that there's only one tally per deployment
amwo_processed <- amwo_data %>% 
  mutate(ind_id = paste(local_identifier, tag_local_identifier))

num <- amwo_processed %>% 
  group_by(ind_id) %>% 
  tally()

hist(num$n, n = 30)
quantile(num$n)
```
